name: Team Green Lawn
overview:
Team Green Lawn offers fertilization and weed control in Dayton,OH

Team Green Lawn is the largest local lawn care company in the Dayton area. One of the most important things when owning a home is having a nice lawn. At Team Green Lawn our goal is to help you achieve just that. From our advanced products to the technicians we train and hire you are guaranteed to have a great looking lawn. We have received outstanding reviews that verify the process we use really works! Our three step process works like this, First we will apply a blanket of fertilizer across the lawn, second spray our broadleaf weed control to kill things, such as dandelions, and finally a spot spray for hard to get weeds like crabgrass. You can see why we have had so many great reviews. If you are in the market for a new lawn service call Team Green Lawn at 937-372-4802 or go to our website at www.teamgreenlawn.com
